1
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,160
Bomb!

2
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,040
Fall back, all of you!

3
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,120
Fall back, all of you!

4
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,360
Retreat!

5
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:51,720
(After the mission, kill Zhao Wudi.)

6
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:05,920
A Di!

7
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:06,960
Get over here and help!

8
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:07,880
It's so heavy!

9
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:11,640
Give up your special forces pipe dream.

10
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,320
A Di!

11
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,240
You amaze me, I swear.

12
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,480
It's a warzone out there.

13
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,680
And you can still sleep?

14
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:19,920
Boss.

15
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,800
The Dongba Code.

16
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:22,920
No matter how big the crisis,

17
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,960
it can't mess with my sleep.

18
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,120
Hurry up and pick the veggies.

19
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,520
Guests will be here to eat soon.

20
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:29,880
Hurry up, hurry up, hurry up!

21
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,160
Quit dragging your feet.

22
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:43,000
Anything else you need?

23
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,040
No... no, that's all.

24
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,960
Bro Kun is here!

25
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,760
Quick, quick, Bro Kun's here!

26
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,880
Welcome, Bro Kun. Please, have a seat.

27
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,600
Bro Kun works for Sis Fei.

28
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,640
Watch yourself.

29
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,320
Bro Kun, there's a chick.

30
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,320
Not bad at all.

31
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:30,880
Nice, nice.

32
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,720
Hey, beautiful.

33
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,200
Come have a drink.

34
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,520
Wudi...

35
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,160
Do you love me?

36
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,440
Zhao Wudi loves Shen Xingyu

37
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,320
for 10,000 years.

38
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,120
Wudi!

39
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,560
I knew you weren't dead.

40
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,440
What the hell is going on?

41
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:04,400
Bro Kun.

42
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,040
Bro Kun, how about you...

43
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,600
Get lost! None of your business!

44
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,840
Beautiful.

45
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,400
You've got the wrong guy.

46
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:17,960
You lost your memory?

47
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,440
Adopted?

48
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,640
You have a twin brother?

49
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:27,360
Why do you look exactly like Zhao Wudi?

50
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,000
Then ask him.

51
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,240
Why does he look like me?

52
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:31,960
Hey, beautiful.

53
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,680
Have a drink with me.

54
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,360
He's just a waiter. Why hang with him?

55
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,600
Roll with me.

56
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,040
I'll make you so happy.

57
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,920
Make your legs shake.

58
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,720
Boss!

59
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,640
Grab this bitch for me!

60
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:49,800
Once I'm done playing with her,

61
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,480
send her to the nightclub.

62
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,760
Let her entertain clients. Go!

63
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,440
A Di has a gun!

64
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:20,520
Hong Ye and Sis Fei set the rules:

65
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:22,480
You can fight in Dongba,

66
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,360
but no guns.

67
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,840
Are you possessed or something?

68
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,080
You dare mess with me?

69
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,560
House rules.

70
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,400
Drinks, 800.

71
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,560
Disrupting business,

72
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:33,920
8,000.

73
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,320
No, no, no need.

74
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:36,440
I'm kidding, I'm kidding.

75
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,920
And... also...

76
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:38,640
Bro Kun.

77
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:41,240
I'll throw in two more bottles of fine liquor.

78
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:41,920
Fine.

79
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,120
Fine.

80
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,480
This chick,

81
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,720
I'm taking her.

82
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,800
Call for backup!

83
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:56,440
We can't let those two scumbags get away!

84
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,320
Call for backup!

85
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,240
A Di!

86
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,160
Go, now!

87
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,920
Once their people show up, we're done!

88
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,840
Take her and go first!

89
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,080
What about you, Boss?

90
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:03,600
I'll be fine.

91
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,000
You two, go! Go now!

92
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,320
Go!

93
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,240
Get in!

94
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,400
I'm coming too.

95
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,720
After them!

96
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,360
I really do look like Zhao Wudi.

97
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:19,160
You remembered?

98
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:19,600
No.

99
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,560
Sit tight.

100
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,160
You really look like my husband.

101
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,280
Beautiful.

102
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,320
What year is it?

103
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,880
That's an old-school way to hit on guys.

104
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,440
Here, a photo of my husband.

105
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,480
Let me see.

106
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,160
Can you drive or not?

107
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,960
It's photoshopped.

108
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,080
It's real.

109
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,760
Absolutely genuine.

110
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,000
My God...

111
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,640
I can't believe two people look so alike.

112
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,000
I'm pretty curious about this.

113
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:24,920
Take it.

114
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,320
Get it tested.

115
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:31,960
Protect me.

116
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,400
I'll give you 50,000.

117
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,320
It's not about money.

118
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,320
Five million.

119
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,240
That's a tough job to take.

120
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,080
Where to?

121
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,240
To see Sis Fei.

122
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,640
We'll settle the Bro Kun situation.

123
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,680
You've got some nerve, kid.

124
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,920
Showing up on my turf.

125
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,480
You got a death wish?

126
00:08:42,920 --> 00:08:44,520
Rule-abiding A Di

127
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,800
dared to hit my man in Dongba Town.

128
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,200
Except for Dawa,

129
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,200
you're the first.

130
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:51,600
Sis Fei.

131
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,800
Someone broke your rules first

132
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,600
and pulled a gun.

133
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,120
That's why I went hard.

134
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:56,920
This matter...

135
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:58,920
you handled it wrong.

136
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,160
Whatever Sis Fei says,

137
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,320
I'll change.

138
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,960
You went too easy.

139
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,200
Breaking the rules

140
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,000
deserves death.

141
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,880
This is a pretty hand.

142
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,960
Leave this hand behind.

143
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,680
Then we'll call it even.

144
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:48,600
Sis Fei

145
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,040
The Dongba Code

146
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,120
I answer for my own actions.

147
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,800
If you've got a problem, come at me

148
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:54,600
She's got nothing to do with it

149
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,040
Since you want to make an enemy

150
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,560
Then do something for me

151
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,240
To spare her hand.

152
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:05,240
Today's General Dawa's birthday

153
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,960
Deliver him a birthday cake

154
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,320
Wish him a happy birthday

155
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,000
And a long and healthy life

156
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,040
Sis Fei

157
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,520
Everyone knows

158
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,680
You and General Dawa don't get along

159
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,920
And you're celebrating his birthday?

160
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,840
Feud or no feud,

161
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,440
basic courtesies must be kept.

162
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,200
I also want to ease tensions while at it.

163
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:27,880
Do I have another option?

164
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,520
You don't have a choice

165
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,320
That's not an ordinary place

166
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,920
You might even see Hong Ye

167
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,200
Thanks for taking that blade for me

168
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,160
Just a scratch

169
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,040
Let's get through what's in front of us first

170
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:50,280
Sis Fei is definitely up to no good

171
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,600
Why don't we just run?

172
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,040
We can't

173
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,480
They've locked onto us.

174
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,720
Snipers

175
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:01,640
Stay calm

176
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:03,680
One each

177
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:08,080
Should we run in a zigzag or straight line?

178
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:11,080
Doesn't matter which route we take

179
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:11,920
Keep up

180
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:19,280
This cake's almost heavier than a rock

181
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,640
It's probably a bomb

182
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,240
So we're still gonna die, aren't we?

183
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,840
I don't know if we'll die later

184
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,440
But if we stop now

185
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:28,920
We're dead for sure

186
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,800
Sis Fei set up an inside man for us

187
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,400
That's why we got in so easily

188
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:52,920
Hold it

189
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:53,680
Routine inspection

190
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:54,840
Come on,

191
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,720
Didn't you just check us?

192
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,600
You're checking again?

193
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:58,600
Safety first

194
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,680
Hold on

195
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:06,760
Ali

196
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,320
They know each other

197
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,640
I'll do it

198
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,520
Wait

199
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,080
Bro

200
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,360
Mind holding this for a sec?

201
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:40,400
Did Ali mistake him for Zhao Wudi

202
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,800
Or is Ali intentionally approaching A Di?

203
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:45,200
Why would she come to Dongba?
